            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit.
            Esse, recusandae. Similique, quidem, consequatur! Facere quod
            exercitationem illo nesciunt minus ex accusantium eligendi tempora
            nihil, officiis, quaerat minima, culpa similique velit...
            <%=
              link_to "more", "#",
              class: "apple-blue"
            %>
          </p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div>
          <h4>Information</h4>
          <table class="table lead">
            <tr>
              <td class="dark-gray">Seller</td>
              <td>Leksi LLC</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="dark-gray">Category</td>
              <td>Education</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="dark-gray">Updated</td>
              <td>Aug 6, 2015</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="dark-gray">Size</td>
              <td>0 MB (nothing to download!)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="dark-gray">Rating</td>
              <td>not enough reviews yet</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="dark-gray">Compatibility</td>
              <td>Works and looks pretty on any device.</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    	<div class="center">
        <br/>
        <br/>
        <br/>
